*Veliku* iznenađenost osećala je svaka osoba u sobi. (Everyone in the room felt a great surprise.)

Ona je imala *veliku* sreću da uspe da uspešno završi posao. (She was very lucky to successfully finish the job.)

Kada je video *veliku* količinu novca, njegovo srce je počelo da brže kuca. (When he saw a great amount of money, his heart started beating faster.)

Oni su bili veoma impresionirani *velikom* kućom u kojoj su boravili. (They were very impressed with the big house they stayed in.)

Ona je učinila *veliku* grešku jer nije čitala uputstva. (She made a big mistake by not reading the instructions.)